Version 0.0.3
=============

* Added support for newer libcdparanoia (access to device name was broken
  before)
* Added support to lowercase ASCII chars in file and dir name when saving
* Added support to replace spaces by underscores in file and dir names
* Fixed bug where '/' char was in meta info and dir/file creation was broken
* Fixed bug where paranoia mode was always set to off

Version 0.0.2
=============

* Added support for command line options
* Bugfix with input of artist
* New config file options: device, multidisc

Version 0.0.1
=============

* Initial Release
